  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>(5 mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p><q>Hoy hicimos torres de cubos que correspondían a cada número. Pusimos las torres y los números en orden</q></p>
<p>Display the cube towers in order from 1–10 with the numbers below each tower.</p>
<p><q>¿Qué observan acerca de las torres y los números?</q> (The towers get bigger as you count. Each tower has one more cube than the one before it. Each number is one more than the number before it.)</p>

